      "width": 360,
      "height": 204,
      "text": "LEGEND\n\n■ Navy (#1B2B4B) Rectangle = Page / Route\n◆ Gold (#C5A55A) Diamond = Decision Point\n◆ Gold (#C5A55A) Rectangle = Pricing / Action\n□ Grey (dashed) = External / Internal / Trigger\n→ Solid arrow = Primary flow\n- - → Dashed arrow = Exit / secondary path\n\n★ Click any navy rectangle to open the live page",
